text: Katherine "Kat" Flores (born October 28, 1987), known professionally as Tatu Baby, is an American tattoo artist and reality television personality. ==On television== She was a contestant on Ink Master season 2 in 2012, where she placed fourth, followed by season 3 of the same show in 2013, where she placed third. She currently stars as a main cast member in Cartel Crew (2019â€“present), another reality television show based on people who have connections to drug cartels. ==As artist== Tatu Baby has remained active as a tattoo artist in Miami, Florida.
